\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

的向量积定义为
\begin_inset Formula $a\times b=(|a||b|\sin\theta)e_{n}$
\end_inset

.
 其中
\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

