\begin_inset Formula $0\leq\theta\leq\pi$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $e_{n}$
\end_inset

垂直于
\begin_inset Formula $a,b$
\end_inset

的单位向量, 其方向为按照右手系从
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

转向
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

决定.
 
\end_layout

